{"type":"message","id":"eab934ee","parentId":"803f2ef4","timestamp":"2026-03-31T00:56:47.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🐉 当前已安装的 OpenClaw 技能列表：\n\n### 官方内置技能\n1. **1password** - 1Password CLI 集成，管理密钥和密码\n2. **apple-notes** - macOS Apple Notes 管理\n3. **apple-reminders** - Apple Reminders 管理\n4. **camsnap** - RTSP/ONVIF 摄像头抓帧\n5. **clawhub** - ClawHub 技能仓库搜索安装更新\n6. **gh-issues** - GitHub Issues 自动修复和 PR 生成\n7. **gifgrep** - GIF 搜索下载工具\n8. **github** - GitHub CLI 操作\n9. **gog** - Google Workspace CLI 集成\n10. **healthcheck** - 主机安全检查和加固\n11. **himalaya** - IMAP/SMTP 邮件管理\n12. **imsg** - iMessage/SMS CLI 集成\n13. **mcporter** - MCP 服务器工具调用\n14. **nano-pdf** - PDF 编辑\n15. **node-connect** - 节点连接诊断\n16. **obsidian** - Obsidian 笔记自动化\n17. **openhue** - Philips Hue 灯光控制\n18. **oracle** - Oracle CLI 使用最佳实践\n19. **peekaboo** - macOS UI 自动化捕获\n20. **skill-creator** - 创建和改进 AgentSkills\n21. **summarize** - 文本/URL/播客摘要\n22. **weather** - 天气查询\n\n### 自定义/工作区技能\n23. **video-frames** - ffmpeg 视频抽帧\n24. **agent-browser** - 无头浏览器自动化\n25. **multimodal-quiz-generator** - 多模态题库生成\n26. **video-gen** - 火山引擎 AI 视频生成\n\n需要我帮你安装某个技能，还是查看某个技能的详细用法？😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":678,"output":446,"cacheRead":17720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774918601308,"responseId":"02177491860139720e33ae3714a969f29832d54235fd2cc922f32"}}
